snippet.title: Turbo: Super Stunt Squad - PS3/X360/WiiU/Wii/3DS/NDS - Trailer!
snippet.description:
Join Team Turbo and perform awesome stunts with Turbo and his crew! Check out the first trailer of the video game based on the upcoming animated film from DreamWorks Animation.

Turbo: Super Stunt Squad will be available on PS3, X360, Wii U, Wii, NDS and 3DS

For more information, please visit your local Namco Bandai website, http://www.namcobandaigames.eu
Talk about this game, share tips & win goodies at http://www.namcobandaigames.eu/community
